For the second issue, if you just want to enable bucket logging, you don't need to add a grant for the log delivery group (more info if you're interested: http://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/dev/enable-logging-programming.html).

So you can just use:

```
    BucketLoggingStatus={
        'LoggingEnabled': {
            'TargetBucket': bucket,
            'TargetPrefix': 'logs/',
        }
    }
```

